entries.s_13: I'm sorry to bother you, but I have nowhere else to turn.
entries.s_16: Yes. It appears to still be working.
entries.s_17: That's better than I could have hoped for! Some of these images are also of people that died in the Clone Wars, and I miss them terribly. This reward seems like far less than you deserve, but it's all I have.
entries.s_18: I hope it isn't gone for good. Sometimes I can still hear them.
entries.s_19: Thank you. May I suggest making copies of your data crystals?
entries.s_20: Yes. I'm going to do that now.
entries.s_25: I lost my datapad. I know that it's not especially valuable to anyone else, but it has images that I cannot replace. Please, get it back!
entries.s_29: Thank you! I was downstairs, near the central room. I was running from those crazy droids down there. Maybe one of them picked it up.
entries.s_35: Sorry, but I can't do anything about that right now.
entries.s_39: I don't have time right now.
entries.s_41: I hope I can find someone to help me.
entries.s_44: I need someone with solid skills. Please come back when you have completed your training.
